title: Fire Commissioner Jenkins announces he will retire; Mayor thanks him for his 29 years of ...
text: ( Source : City of Detroit , MI) After 29 years of service to the Detroit Fire Department , Executive Fire Commissioner has announced his decision to retire effective Friday, Oct 16 . Jenkins said he was honored to lead the Department he served
